# Cloudflare Pages — files to skip at upload time. Same syntax as .gitignore.
#
# The 4 book artifacts (51-53M each) exceed Pages' 25 MiB-per-file limit and
# are served from R2 via the edge-redirect in `_redirects`. The 0-byte
# `toPdfViaTempFile*.pdf` is a build-time leftover that should never have
# been committed; ignored here so it doesn't ride along to production.
bipartitebook/downloads/The_Bipartite_Universe.epub
bipartitebook/downloads/The_Bipartite_Universe_BW.pdf
bipartitebook/downloads/The_Bipartite_Universe_Color.pdf
bipartitebook/downloads/The_Bipartite_Universe_Dyslexia.pdf
bipartitebook/downloads/toPdfViaTempFile*.pdf
